SOS AMERICA GOD BLESS AMERICA
America, we most all come together as one to fight the Corona-virus before it is to late. We can not allow UNCERTAINTY, FEAR, PANIC, or ARROGANCE drive us towards failure. We know and understand what needs to be done to stop the virus from spreading and yet we are not doing enough ourselves to stop the spread witch is threatening our families, friends, love ones and worst of all our nation's future and way of life. America's TOP world power status is no accident, strong leadership and decisions are always necessary but what really has kept this country strong and well is our people's valor and response to aid our own, the self determent brave men and women (leaders) who always rise to the occasion to fight endlessly to protect our freedom no matter the sacrifice. The Corona-virus has called the world and America to war... YES, THE WORLD IS AT WAR! This isn't a military war operation, but it is every american's HEALTH WAR to fight. It is our individual duty to protect the interest of first our country, and then the world. We must all do our part to QUICKLY solve the health crisis here at home so we can then move on to help the rest of the world recover as it is also in our best interest for the world to recover quickly before tensions rise out of control. America, waiting any further is not only inhuman to our own but its also reckless and a great deal of risk to our public infrastructure and national security and overall survival. As this virus pandemic continues to spread over the world more people will die, governments will collapse, and the world will be full of poverty, hunger, devastation, and CIVIL wars. We must stop the spread now before we are compromise/sick or to weak to defend any possible security threat towards our nation, freedom and way of life. I believe our military should be kept away, healthy and ready to respond to any foreign national security issues. I know we can handle this pandemic our self if we work together and I believe it can all be done smoothly if we can all get in the same mind set and plan.






QUICK EASY IDEAS:
#1 Let's create a FREE mobile application for all individual and families to easily share there current health condition real time. This will help us get more accurate real time data about who might possibly be sick with the virus, where the test are mostly needed and where the next wave will be the hardest. This can be easily done, most people have smartphones, tables, or computers, and it will help assist the ones in urgent need with there needs so they can stay indoors and away from others while they get better.


#2 Let's create neighbors zero contact assistance groups. There are many needs that we as a community can individually work on to help others who are either sick or caring for others.


#3 We need anti viral cleaning chemicals to be available to everyone now and for any open business to leave there door open so the public can enter with out touching.


#4 We need antiviral sprays at all gas pumps, or someone dedicated to pumping each customers gas with out any contact.


#5 We need to temporarily only allow customers to make there purchases online and allow access to very few people per store every other hr, cleaning and spraying in-between.


WHAT DO YOU THINK ???
PLEASE SHARE!



GOD BLESS AMERICA!
